trans-unit.source: The example companies, organizations, products, domain names, e-mail addresses, logos, people, places, and events depicted herein are fictitious.

trans-unit.source: No association with any real company, organization, product, domain name, e-mail address, logo, person, places, or events is intended or should be inferred.
trans-unit.target: No se pretende establecer ni se debe inferir ninguna asociación con ninguna empresa, organización, producto, nombre de dominio, dirección de correo electrónico, logotipo, persona, lugar ni evento real.
